g src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T17:41:13.000Z","msg":"吳若希就唔好拎出黎講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd45fac4590f0948ff1d48b38eef47d7e5a7713","tid":1954081,"uid":279814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T18:30:43.000Z","msg":"其實兩個去到後期唱歌已入化境<br />\n唱到好自然 好似耳邊講嘢咁 <br />\n但講音樂 都係eason了<br />\neason 把聲得天獨厚<br />\nRange寛得黎充滿力量同質感<br />\n就算高音都唔會失真變薄<br />\n而且成個樂壇最好既歌都俾曬佢唱咁<br />\n養肥曬 <br />\n所以eason略高一籌"},{"pid":"a5b1c52da357a912b9955c587c690ea44a65207e","tid":1954081,"uid":53855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f45fe659c89797dc811059fb56a815078e88754","tid":1954081,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅算香港代表啦  <br />\n<br />\n係幾勁  <br />\n<br />\n不過始終去唔到再高階段<br />\n<br />\n佢好似唔識作曲編曲<br />\n<br />\n唱歌真係頂級"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:16:09.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅識作曲。"},{"pid":"e85f912ac98fb33606d7b72df8a6d97fcf7fcbd1","tid":1954081,"uid":183058,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:25:06.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅 三次 台灣金曲獎最佳男歌手  最佳國語專輯<br />\n<br />\n張國榮 一次 都沒 入圍 吧？<br />\n<br />\n台灣金曲獎1990年 開設 的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS：陳奕迅香港音樂獎項更多，但2000年後香港四大音樂頒獎禮基本是垃圾，所以無意義提出。"},{"pid":"ea1c226a0d17093b1bfd3c4cfb8d25bedf75be67","tid":1954081,"uid":33929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5b1c52da357a912b9955c587c690ea44a65207e","tid":1954081,"uid":53855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f45fe659c89797dc811059fb56a815078e88754","tid":1954081,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅算香港代表啦  <br />\n<br />\n係幾勁  <br />\n<br />\n不過始終去唔到再高階段<br />\n<br />\n佢好似唔識作曲編曲<br />\n<br />\n唱歌真係頂級"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:16:09.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅識作曲。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01